1
00:00:12,090 --> 00:00:16,140
[2012]

2
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,640
Is this your girl?

3
00:00:48,670 --> 00:00:49,670
Give it back to me!

4
00:00:50,030 --> 00:00:51,200
Give it back to me!

5
00:01:03,670 --> 00:01:05,330
Everyone, search carefully.

6
00:01:05,349 --> 00:01:06,870
There should be a pocket watch.

7
00:01:06,870 --> 00:01:07,950
Yes!

8
00:01:38,070 --> 00:01:40,229
Protect Zhou Jin.

9
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,350
I must protect Zhou Jin.

10
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:45,430
I promise you.

11
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,229
I promise you, okay?

12
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:16,190
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

13
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:18,810
[Episode 23]

14
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,240
Command vehicle!

15
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:37,400
Junior, we need firefighter backup.

16
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,190
You can't go there! It's dangerous!

17
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:39,840
Zhou!

18
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,310
Hansheng!

19
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,470
Calm down, Junior.

20
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,850
You can't go over there, Zhou!

21
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:47,280
Zhou!

22
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:47,880
Hansheng!

23
00:03:47,970 --> 00:03:48,690
Zhou!

24
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,470
Hansheng!

25
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,990
Calm down, Junior!

26
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,000
Hansheng!

27
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:56,710
Zhou!

28
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,079
Hansheng!

29
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,430
Calm down, Junior!

30
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:01,360
You can't go over there!

31
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,080
Hansheng!

32
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,520
Zhou Jin, stay calm!

33
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,120
Hansheng!

34
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:04,870
Junior!

35
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:05,680
Hansheng!

36
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:06,980
Junior, calm down!

37
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:08,400
Zhou Jin!

38
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,830
Why didn't you knock?

39
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,830
The door wasn't locked.

40
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,050
Hospital room doors don't have locks.

41
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,370
Are you feeling better?

42
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,510
I'm okay.

43
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:55,150
What exactly do you mean?

44
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:02,390
Zhou Jin.

45
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,930
Let's keep some distance between us.

46
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,130
So you still want a divorce.

47
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:20,960
What's your reason?

48
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,130
If it's because of Jiang Cheng...

49
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:33,750
Jiang Hansheng,

50
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,430
you know me.

51
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:39,450
Whether it's marriage

52
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,800
or love,

53
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,240
I'm not a casual person.

54
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:55,890
So here's the deal.

55
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,600
If you say

56
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:59,120
that you hate me,

57
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:02,040
I'll sign the divorce papers right away.

58
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,830
You can keep your car and house,

59
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,560
and we'll go our separate ways.

60
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:21,010
Do you really

61
00:07:21,010 --> 00:07:22,810
have no feelings for me anymore?

62
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:27,360
Do you dare to say it?

63
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,270
Zhou Jin.

64
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,500
You don't understand.

65
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:41,480
I really don't understand.

66
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,440
If you tell me, won't I understand?

67
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,480
You should have the right to choose.

68
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,610
Jiang Cheng was in prison at that time.

69
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:57,080
He couldn't tell you what he was doing.

70
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,580
He could only let you hate him.

71
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,240
You had no choice.

72
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:04,270
When I was helping you with the case,

73
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,000
I never asked you

74
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,810
if you actually needed my help either.

75
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:10,800
I was too selfish.

76
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,190
I forced my way into your life.

77
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,480
That's not fair to you, Zhou Jin.

78
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:20,690
You should have the chance to choose,

79
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,870
knowing all the facts.

80
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:28,040
I already know everything.

81
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:32,080
I still don't want to change anything.

82
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:37,549
There are still many things
you don't know.

83
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,150
Zhou Jin.

84
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,570
You don't really know me at all.

85
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,770
Haven't you been asking

86
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:47,000
why I can always find you?

87
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,530
Because I've been following you.

88
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:57,790
Ma'am, give me a steamed bun.

89
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:58,670
Okay.

90
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:02,550
How about a tea egg too?

91
00:09:02,570 --> 00:09:02,930
Sure.

92
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:05,750
Five years ago,

93
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:08,220
when we went to arrest Qi Yan,

94
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:11,200
he stole my pocket watch.

95
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,360
Inside the watch

96
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,550
was your photo.

97
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:18,320
Those people have seen what you look like.

98
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,550
Although I always thought Qi Yan was dead,

99
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:22,030
I still felt uneasy.

100
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:24,330
I was afraid that someone else

101
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:25,440
might try to get revenge on me

102
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,320
by finding you

103
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:29,140
and doing something crazy to you.

104
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:44,740
♪ I should never have let you bear this ♪

105
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:52,490
♪ I always want to give you
everything I have ♪

106
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:59,740
♪ If only it could win your heart,
even for a moment ♪

107
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:03,490
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

108
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:07,310
♪ They're so free ♪

109
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:14,800
♪ I never want to see you hang your head ♪

110
00:10:17,970 --> 00:10:21,040
♪ I keep dreaming of
what lies ahead for us ♪

111
00:10:25,310 --> 00:10:29,250
♪ If only it could keep us
in love forever ♪

112
00:10:29,780 --> 00:10:33,010
♪ Look at the zebras ♪

113
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:36,300
♪ How freely they swim ♪

114
00:10:38,210 --> 00:10:41,280
♪ How can I tell you ♪

115
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:44,940
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

116
00:10:45,610 --> 00:10:48,430
♪ I am sure to ♪

117
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:52,010
♪ Walk with you ♪

118
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:56,510
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

119
00:10:56,530 --> 00:11:00,660
♪ One more glance is not enough ♪

120
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,900
♪ At the crossroad ♪

121
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:06,300
♪ To the left or right ♪

122
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:11,220
♪ I want to hold your hand ♪

123
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,320
Qi Yan used me

124
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,900
to threaten you,

125
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:21,320
so for these three years,

126
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,780
you've always been by my side?

127
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,080
If I couldn't see that you were safe,

128
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,210
my heart would be in constant anxiety,

129
00:11:33,510 --> 00:11:35,710
and I wouldn't be able to live normally.

130
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,440
Later when the pocket watch disappeared,

131
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:42,440
you were afraid I might be in danger,

132
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,920
so you came to Haizhou

133
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,630
to keep protecting me?

134
00:11:47,890 --> 00:11:48,550
That pocket watch

135
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:50,610
belonged to your brother Zhou Chuan.

136
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,600
I remember.

137
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,080
My brother won it

138
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:08,510
as a prize in a sniper competition.

139
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,580
Your brother gave it to me.

140
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:18,530
I really treasured it.

141
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,030
I asked my brother for it before.

142
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:24,430
He wouldn't give it to me.

143
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,600
He told me mysteriously

144
00:12:28,870 --> 00:12:30,070
that he gave the watch

145
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,750
to someone

146
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,560
who needed it more than I did.

147
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,080
It was you?

148
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,360
Yes.

149
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:57,000
How can someone like you exist?

150
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,010
Jiang Hansheng.

151
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,480
I'm sorry.

152
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,240
"I'm sorry."

153
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:08,250
You're always apologizing to me.

154
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:17,040
I loved you too obsessively.

155
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,490
Obsessive to the point
of being despicable.

156
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,630
At first,

157
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,550
I just wanted to watch you from afar

158
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:25,950
and that would be enough.

159
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,360
But as time went on,

160
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,230
I wanted you to notice me too.

161
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,880
And once I had the chance,

162
00:13:35,530 --> 00:13:37,130
I even hoped I could have you.

163
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:40,190
Zhou Jin, I was so afraid.

164
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:44,540
I was terrified you'd see my selfish side

165
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,520
and start to hate me.

166
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,320
I know I shouldn't get close to you.

167
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,420
Being close to you
would only bring you pain.

168
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:56,960
I'm sorry.

169
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:12,480
Then from now on,

170
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,960
stop loving me.

171
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:23,750
Okay.

172
00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:36,150
Jiang Hansheng,

173
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,930
how can someone like you exist?

174
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:44,440
From now on,

175
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,060
you don't need to love me anymore.

176
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,130
Let me love you instead.

177
00:14:53,210 --> 00:14:54,480
I will always love you.

178
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:57,890
I'll love you until...

179
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,870
you stop hating yourself.

180
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:03,240
Okay?

181
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,360
Zhou Jin.

182
00:15:14,790 --> 00:15:16,120
Let's not get divorced.

183
00:15:17,390 --> 00:15:18,150
Okay?

184
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:20,510
Zhou Jin.

185
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,480
I might not be able to
take good care of you.

186
00:15:25,510 --> 00:15:28,110
I haven't taken good care
of you before either.

187
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,320
From now on,

188
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,620
we'll take care of each other.

189
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,710
We'll grow together.

190
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:37,600
Okay?

191
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:42,590
I want to be good to you.

192
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,370
I want to love you properly.

193
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,650
If you want the moon,

194
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:53,320
I'll never settle for giving you stars.

195
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:55,870
Is that okay?

196
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,550
If you don't agree,

197
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,760
I have other ways to win you over.

198
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,730
I'm quite good at it anyway.

199
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,160
Why are you good at it?

200
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:16,050
What are you thinking?

201
00:16:16,510 --> 00:16:18,240
It's not what you're thinking.

202
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,730
Then I'll have to use

203
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:25,830
my special tactics just for you.

204
00:16:27,770 --> 00:16:29,770
Don't think I don't understand you.

205
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:48,720
Jiang Hansheng.

206
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,480
You're blushing.

207
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:56,450
Is it okay for me to win you over

208
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:57,790
like this?

209
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:02,730
Do you still want a divorce?

210
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:05,079
Zhou Jin.

211
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,349
I love you.

212
00:17:14,410 --> 00:17:15,329
Zhou!

213
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:17,069
Is this the right room?

214
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:18,270
It should be.

215
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:19,950
Let's go in.

216
00:17:23,829 --> 00:17:24,510
How are you?

217
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:26,200
Feeling better?

218
00:17:27,339 --> 00:17:28,099
Zhou Jin.

219
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,330
whose hospital bed is this?

220
00:17:29,330 --> 00:17:31,720
Get down. So inappropriate.

221
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:33,200
Take it easy.

222
00:17:36,130 --> 00:17:36,570
Dad.

223
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:40,710
You look much better.

224
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,640
You're recovering well.

225
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,480
Are you feeling better?

226
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:43,960
Not bad.

227
00:17:45,060 --> 00:17:46,020
In the future,

228
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:48,010
don't indulge Zhou Jin.

229
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:49,510
With her personality,

230
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:51,170
she easily gets into trouble.

231
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,700
I'm talking about you.

232
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:54,850
Who do you think you are?

233
00:17:54,850 --> 00:17:56,850
How dare you jump out of a moving car?

234
00:17:57,150 --> 00:17:58,480
Do you have a death wish?

235
00:17:59,110 --> 00:17:59,550
Dad,

236
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,310
this isn't Zhou Jin's fault.

237
00:18:01,310 --> 00:18:02,110
It's my fault.

238
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,440
I couldn't stop her.

239
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:04,690
I'm scolding her,

240
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:06,510
and you're still defending her?

241
00:18:06,790 --> 00:18:09,200
I'm not worried about Zhou Jin.
She's full of energy.

242
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:09,960
But you,

243
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:11,590
you were seriously injured.

244
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,920
You must rest properly.

245
00:18:13,140 --> 00:18:14,720
It's nothing, Mom. Just a minor injury.

246
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:15,780
I'll recover soon.

247
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:17,420
You still need to watch your nutrition.

248
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:19,350
I'll make some soup for you tonight

249
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,640
and bring it over.

250
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:22,240
Thanks, Mom.

251
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,070
I want some too.

252
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:27,250
You want my snakehead fish soup too?

253
00:18:28,270 --> 00:18:28,870
No thanks.

254
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:32,240
Zhou Jin,

255
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:33,830
about your work,

256
00:18:33,850 --> 00:18:35,030
I need to say a few more words.

257
00:18:35,030 --> 00:18:36,680
That's enough. Stop lecturing her.

258
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:37,590
Hey, I'm just concerned about her.

259
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:38,030
Dad,

260
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,240
don't worry.

261
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,030
I'll look after her from now on.

262
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:41,590
Good.

263
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:44,610
Hearing you say that puts my mind at ease.

264
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,550
My dad loves to nag.

265
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,840
He's making my head spin.

266
00:19:47,170 --> 00:19:48,100
You really came.

267
00:19:52,130 --> 00:19:53,510
Are you avoiding Zhou Jin

268
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:55,000
or her parents?

269
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:56,240
No.

270
00:19:57,420 --> 00:19:58,680
I just felt suffocated

271
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,560
and came here to get some air.

272
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:06,060
They've all gone back?

273
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:12,000
The elderly couple insisted on
coming to the station.

274
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:14,290
Seems like unless they saw you
with their own eyes,

275
00:20:14,290 --> 00:20:15,690
they wouldn't be at ease.

276
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:17,960
Their things are at my place,

277
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,420
but they've already left.

278
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,480
I told them

279
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,830
that you're now

280
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:23,030
a key witness.

281
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:25,430
You need to be questioned

282
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:28,070
and also need special protection,

283
00:20:28,070 --> 00:20:29,870
so you're being kept in custody.

284
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,920
Anyway, whatever needs to be discussed

285
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,120
can wait until later.

286
00:20:33,270 --> 00:20:35,200
I won't really be locked up, will I?

287
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,180
Zhou Jin is doing well.

288
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:39,880
She'll be discharged soon.

289
00:20:40,550 --> 00:20:41,400
I told her

290
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:44,540
that until the higher-ups
make an official decision,

291
00:20:44,540 --> 00:20:46,140
I'll be responsible for you.

292
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:48,140
She doesn't need to worry.

293
00:20:51,010 --> 00:20:53,340
There's no trace of Qi Yan
and Qiu Ye at all?

294
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,160
That's exactly

295
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:00,490
why I needed to find you.

296
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,200
Think carefully.

297
00:21:02,790 --> 00:21:03,920
Is there anyone else

298
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,910
who might know his whereabouts?

299
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,290
Now, Qi is

300
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,680
absolutely determined.

301
00:21:11,550 --> 00:21:13,010
He won't say a single word.

302
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,080
If this continues,

303
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,690
all our efforts will be wasted.

304
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,980
We need to think of another approach.

305
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:29,960
It's getting late.

306
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:30,760
Get in the car.

307
00:21:30,790 --> 00:21:32,190
I'll take you home first.

308
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,100
I actually quite like it here.

309
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:09,080
After Leader Yao's sacrifice,

310
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:10,840
I know you're feeling down.

311
00:22:12,790 --> 00:22:14,250
I understand how you feel.

312
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:18,440
Before,

313
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,030
I always met with Yao here.

314
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:25,610
Sometimes we'd meet down on those rocks,

315
00:22:25,640 --> 00:22:26,510
where it's pitch black,

316
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:28,110
each of us with a flashlight.

317
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:31,320
Sometimes we'd just sit
like we were just now.

318
00:22:32,110 --> 00:22:33,070
Once,

319
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:33,960
during the day,

320
00:22:34,750 --> 00:22:36,680
we pretended to be open-water swimmers

321
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,240
and talked while swimming.

322
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,200
All of this

323
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:45,020
feels like it was just yesterday.

324
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,110
Chief Tan.

325
00:22:51,750 --> 00:22:53,280
It's been almost six years.

326
00:22:53,830 --> 00:22:55,290
Everything that could be done,

327
00:22:55,290 --> 00:22:56,220
I've done it all.

328
00:22:58,830 --> 00:22:59,640
I believe you.

329
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:02,030
You did your best.

330
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:03,480
Yes,

331
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,570
I did try my best.

332
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:08,240
But Yao is gone.

333
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,330
Zhou Jin is gone too.

334
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:14,530
The most ridiculous thing
is that even Old Scorpion is gone.

335
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,200
Six years.

336
00:23:17,560 --> 00:23:18,960
I've worked for nothing.

337
00:23:19,910 --> 00:23:21,070
Don't say that.

338
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,720
Actually, we all understand clearly.

339
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:28,310
The illegal trading chain

340
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,880
that uses Hengyun as its base

341
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:31,740
of operations,

342
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:34,050
which is also what Leader Yao called

343
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:35,300
the Jin-Hai Line,

344
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:37,690
is gradually becoming clear.

345
00:23:38,020 --> 00:23:40,510
The upstream suppliers
and downstream buyers

346
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:42,370
have all shown their true colors.

347
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:44,310
Your contribution was essential.

348
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:46,370
But Old Scorpion hasn't been caught.

349
00:23:46,550 --> 00:23:48,210
All of this will happen again.

350
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:50,550
Five years ago, there was the 8/17 Case.

351
00:23:50,550 --> 00:23:51,970
Now there's the Jingang Wharf.

352
00:23:51,970 --> 00:23:53,080
What about next time?

353
00:23:53,080 --> 00:23:54,480
What will it be next time?

354
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,910
Do you have any new ideas?

355
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:10,260
I'm tired.

356
00:24:27,940 --> 00:24:29,490
As soon as they heard
Qi was arrested,

357
00:24:29,490 --> 00:24:31,550
all his underlings started to crack.

358
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:32,390
It's natural.

359
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,680
They were only afraid of their boss.

360
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:36,640
Now one after another,

361
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:37,720
they're all rushing to confess.

362
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,780
Careful, it's hot.

363
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:41,400
Did they mention Qi Yan?

364
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:43,970
You hit the nail on the head.

365
00:24:43,970 --> 00:24:45,960
Whether he's Qi Yan or Old Scorpion,

366
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:47,490
he's vanished into thin air.

367
00:24:47,490 --> 00:24:48,520
The regular underlings

368
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:49,500
aren't high enough in the ranks

369
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,500
to provide any useful information.

370
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:54,200
Only Qi could get close to him.

371
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,480
But this guy

372
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:58,790
hasn't said a word
since he was brought in.

373
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:01,070
The old fox is keeping his mouth shut.

374
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:02,030
I'm thinking

375
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:03,830
that if we want to find him,

376
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:06,310
we need to try other approaches.

377
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:08,070
Okay, got it.

378
00:25:08,630 --> 00:25:09,260
Good.

379
00:25:09,860 --> 00:25:10,790
I'll hang up now.

380
00:25:19,990 --> 00:25:20,910
Tell Mom for me

381
00:25:21,130 --> 00:25:23,730
that I finished all the soup.
It was delicious.

382
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:26,550
Do you think Qi Yan

383
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:30,150
will really disappear
for five or six years

384
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:31,840
and then make a comeback?

385
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,480
We still have a trump card up our sleeve.

386
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:37,740
We're not afraid of him not reappearing.

387
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:39,110
Qi Zhen?

388
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,950
But will she help the police?

389
00:25:42,550 --> 00:25:44,080
Besides, Qi Yan is a madman.

390
00:25:44,790 --> 00:25:46,000
If we provoke him,

391
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:49,310
more people could get hurt.

392
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:53,010
Using Qi Zhen as our trump card

393
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:55,350
to break down Qi Yan's
psychological defenses

394
00:25:55,350 --> 00:25:56,960
is the most effective approach

395
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:58,220
but also the riskiest.

396
00:25:59,030 --> 00:26:01,430
We can't gamble with other people's lives.

397
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:04,000
Then who is this trump card
you're talking about?

398
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:04,920
Prof recently found

399
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:07,200
a new witness in
the Huaiguang serial murder cases—

400
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,260
Chen Li's ex-wife.

401
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:10,310
Chen Li's ex-wife?

402
00:26:14,130 --> 00:26:15,060
Back then,

403
00:26:16,350 --> 00:26:18,480
I was the one who collected that money.

404
00:26:22,590 --> 00:26:23,200
Go on.

405
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:26,130
Before Chen Li turned himself in,

406
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:27,720
he came to see me.

407
00:26:30,110 --> 00:26:31,840
He was very emotional that day.

408
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:35,830
He talked more than he ever did before.

409
00:26:36,860 --> 00:26:39,080
He said he was mediocre and incompetent,

410
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:41,080
that he failed to be a good husband

411
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:42,550
or a good father.

412
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:44,350
Finally,

413
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,110
he said over these years,

414
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:49,520
he had secretly saved up some money

415
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:52,800
and someone would deliver it
to our home in a few days.

416
00:26:53,850 --> 00:26:56,110
He told me that once I received the money,

417
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:59,150
I should take our son
and leave the country.

418
00:26:59,600 --> 00:27:01,750
I was very surprised at the time.

419
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,200
But at that time,

420
00:27:06,110 --> 00:27:07,570
we were already divorced.

421
00:27:08,270 --> 00:27:09,930
He wouldn't tell me anything,

422
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:12,380
and I couldn't get much more out of him.

423
00:27:16,380 --> 00:27:18,060
How did you get this money?

424
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,310
A few days later,

425
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,310
a group of people

426
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:23,750
came to our home.

427
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:27,160
They said they were entrusted by Chen Li

428
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:29,920
and gave me an offshore account.

429
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,960
And some cash.

430
00:27:36,520 --> 00:27:38,300
Their leader

431
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:39,920
was a young man,

432
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:41,880
about 20 years old,

433
00:27:42,350 --> 00:27:43,510
wearing a suit.

434
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,770
He looked like a gentleman.

435
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:47,640
He didn't speak,

436
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:50,110
but I could tell

437
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:52,400
that the others, though older,

438
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:54,400
all followed his lead.

439
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:56,050
He didn't say a word?

440
00:27:58,570 --> 00:27:59,770
You're a good mother.

441
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,050
For your son's sake,

442
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:05,980
don't say anything unnecessary.

443
00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:08,020
After you leave,

444
00:28:09,510 --> 00:28:10,660
don't come back.

445
00:28:12,990 --> 00:28:13,840
Understand?

446
00:28:16,410 --> 00:28:17,810
That's all he said.

447
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,110
Not long after that,

448
00:28:20,110 --> 00:28:21,270
I saw in the newspaper

449
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:23,200
that Chen Li had turned himself in.

450
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:26,040
Without thinking too much,

451
00:28:26,790 --> 00:28:29,190
I pretty much understood
what was going on.

452
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:30,920
Later,

453
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,350
Officer Wang, you came

454
00:28:33,350 --> 00:28:35,350
to ask me about Chen Li's situation.

455
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,070
At that time,

456
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:39,120
I didn't dare say a word more

457
00:28:39,620 --> 00:28:41,480
for fear of getting into trouble.

458
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:43,720
After all, my son was still young then.

459
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:45,730
Then why did you come back?

460
00:28:48,030 --> 00:28:49,830
Carrying a secret for too long

461
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,330
doesn't lighten it.

462
00:28:52,430 --> 00:28:54,760
Instead, it becomes heavier and heavier.

463
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:57,960
I came back this time

464
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,680
to make some amends.

465
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:03,640
I didn't expect

466
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:05,660
you would find me so quickly.

467
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:12,310
Did you show them Qi Yan's photo?

468
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:13,510
Yes.

469
00:29:14,240 --> 00:29:15,770
They said it looks like him.

470
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:16,910
But you think

471
00:29:17,710 --> 00:29:18,920
he was not Qi Yan,

472
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:19,890
right?

473
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:24,740
Qi Zhen's life was really difficult.

474
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:26,240
If Qi Yan lived with her,

475
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,330
he couldn't possibly have had
that much money.

476
00:29:28,330 --> 00:29:29,200
Even if he did,

477
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:32,030
it would be impossible
to tie up all those loose ends

478
00:29:32,030 --> 00:29:33,550
to tie up all those loose ends.

479
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:35,550
Qi Yan barely went to school as a kid,

480
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,440
let alone arrange for someone
to take the blame,

481
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,200
flee abroad,

482
00:29:38,290 --> 00:29:40,150
and eliminate all consequences.

483
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:42,370
He couldn't have done it alone.

484
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,940
To accomplish all this

485
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:47,170
requires more than just money.

486
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:48,510
It also takes
certain connections and power.

487
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:49,160
So that means

488
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,790
we can draw two conclusions.

489
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:51,590
First,

490
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:54,440
the person Chen Li's ex-wife met

491
00:29:55,130 --> 00:29:56,200
worked with Qi Yan.

492
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:57,110
Second,

493
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,250
this person,

494
00:29:58,310 --> 00:29:59,630
despite being young,

495
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,750
had extensive social resources

496
00:30:01,750 --> 00:30:02,950
and powerful backing

497
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,960
that shouldn't be underestimated.

498
00:30:08,930 --> 00:30:11,260
Do you remember what Yu Liang said before?

499
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:13,270
That Qi Zhen always had hallucinations

500
00:30:13,270 --> 00:30:15,670
about someone trying to take her children?

501
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,670
Perhaps Qi Zhen's hallucinations

502
00:30:18,670 --> 00:30:20,000
weren't just delusions

503
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,530
but actually happened.

504
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:23,650
Back then, she gave birth to twins

505
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:25,340
and for some unknown reason,

506
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:27,590
she left the children's biological father.

507
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:30,160
After that, someone kept fighting her
for custody of the children.

508
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:30,760
In the end,

509
00:30:31,170 --> 00:30:33,030
one child was taken by the father,

510
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:33,950
while the other

511
00:30:33,950 --> 00:30:35,680
remained hidden with the mother.

512
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,560
If we think about it this way,

513
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:37,820
it all makes sense now.

514
00:30:38,330 --> 00:30:40,050
Indeed, no one has ever

515
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,970
mentioned Qi Yan's father.

516
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:45,480
Maybe he's the key to all this.

517
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,130
Twenty years ago...

518
00:30:49,310 --> 00:30:52,310
Twenty years ago,
the twins had just entered society.

519
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:53,890
He must be the one

520
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:57,000
with enough power
to orchestrate everything.

521
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:59,090
Qi Yan committed terrible crimes.

522
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:01,590
This brother
who stayed with their biological father

523
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:03,320
helped cover up all his crimes,

524
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:04,990
including making Chen Li

525
00:31:04,990 --> 00:31:06,250
take the blame for him.

526
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:09,000
After everything was taken care of,

527
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,000
he brought Qi Yan

528
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,890
back to their biological father.

529
00:31:12,190 --> 00:31:13,080
So Qi Yan

530
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,380
also gained powerful backing

531
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,350
and later became Old Scorpion.

532
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,350
If we think about it this way,

533
00:31:19,350 --> 00:31:20,750
everything makes sense.

534
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,310
What kind of person

535
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:25,180
is this brother of his?

536
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:29,030
He and Chen Li's ex-wife

537
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:30,860
only exchanged one sentence.

538
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:32,770
She said on the surface,

539
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,530
he seemed like a gentleman.

540
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:37,440
That's all the information we have.

541
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:42,060
Jiang Cheng mentioned before

542
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,640
that people around Qi Yan

543
00:31:44,750 --> 00:31:46,490
all called him Young Master Wen.

544
00:31:46,490 --> 00:31:47,420
Do you remember?

545
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:49,680
Young Master Wen?

546
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:53,000
I've never heard anyone else
call him Qi Yan.

547
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:54,240
People close to him

548
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,990
all call him Young Master Wen..

549
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:57,590
It seems like some kind of honorific

550
00:31:57,590 --> 00:31:58,640
or a nickname.

551
00:31:59,450 --> 00:32:00,720
So in our minds,

552
00:32:01,060 --> 00:32:03,030
the Qi Yan in the warehouse
is already dead.

553
00:32:03,030 --> 00:32:04,130
But this Young Master Wen

554
00:32:04,130 --> 00:32:04,990
is still alive.

555
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:25,010
Stop thinking about it.

556
00:32:25,070 --> 00:32:26,070
You're tired too.

557
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:28,310
Get some rest.

558
00:32:29,750 --> 00:32:30,750
Brush your teeth,

559
00:32:31,070 --> 00:32:32,600
take a shower, and go to bed.

560
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:41,410
Go to sleep now.

561
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:03,900
We haven't slept together for days.

562
00:33:03,900 --> 00:33:05,770
Move over. Hurry up.

563
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,400
Professor Jiang,

564
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:42,750
the person you shot
and killed back then...

565
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:44,830
Who was it?

566
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:47,770
Of course I know.

567
00:33:48,510 --> 00:33:50,170
that you don't want to die now.

568
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,270
You must be thinking

569
00:33:53,410 --> 00:33:54,920
that if you died now,

570
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:58,450
what would happen
to the girl you care about most?

571
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,640
What's wrong, Hansheng?

572
00:34:03,790 --> 00:34:05,120
Are you feeling unwell?

573
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:05,960
It's nothing.

574
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:07,380
Did you have a nightmare?

575
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:20,449
After I'm discharged,

576
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,360
I want to formally request

577
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:24,090
an extended leave from school.

578
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:25,920
For how long?

579
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,070
A whole semester?

580
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,960
Until Qi Yan is caught.

581
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:38,830
If the school doesn't agree,

582
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,440
I might have to resign.

583
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:42,889
Will Professor Wang

584
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:44,670
be upset?

585
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:47,510
After all, he recommended you
to the position.

586
00:34:47,510 --> 00:34:48,400
No, he won't.

587
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:50,960
He understands me best.

588
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:55,250
Then I support you too.

589
00:34:56,870 --> 00:34:58,530
I understand you best as well.

590
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:20,250
Jiang Hansheng.

591
00:35:23,030 --> 00:35:24,030
How did you always

592
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,710
manage to find me?

593
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:29,850
I installed a tracking system

594
00:35:30,190 --> 00:35:31,550
on your phone,

595
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,400
and in your ring.

596
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,440
That's going too far!

597
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:38,070
I know.

598
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:40,710
I know it wasn't right.

599
00:35:41,290 --> 00:35:41,930
I'm sorry.

600
00:35:43,030 --> 00:35:44,160
When did you do this?

601
00:35:46,150 --> 00:35:46,760
August.

602
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:51,810
The day we visited your brother's grave,

603
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,730
I found the pocket watch

604
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:55,010
next to the tombstone.

605
00:35:56,710 --> 00:35:58,110
Them returning the watch

606
00:35:58,630 --> 00:36:00,690
was nothing but a declaration of war.

607
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,560
I've dealt with them before.

608
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:05,400
One slip-up

609
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,590
could lead to irreversible consequences.

610
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:10,190
So while you were showering,

611
00:36:11,630 --> 00:36:13,510
I messed with your phone

612
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,840
and your ring.

613
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:18,480
Hansheng.

614
00:36:20,890 --> 00:36:22,620
I'll freshen up. Won't be long.

615
00:36:23,510 --> 00:36:24,190
No rush.

616
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:48,040
Can you keep wearing it?

617
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:50,110
After we catch Qi Yan,

618
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:52,100
you can take it off if you want.

619
00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:57,120
Alright.

620
00:36:57,990 --> 00:36:59,050
Let's do that then.

621
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:01,760
I don't want you to

622
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,090
worry too much about me.

623
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,560
The ring doesn't also

624
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:09,480
have listening capabilities, does it?

625
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,720
I didn't go that far.

626
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:13,590
Really?

627
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:18,710
Fine.

628
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,880
I hope we can catch

629
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,780
Qi Yan before the New Year.

630
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:35,800
We will.

631
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:45,220
Good night.

632
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:48,670
Good night.

633
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:49,000
Neither of them like to smile in photos.

634
00:39:11,580 --> 00:39:12,140
Zhou Jin.

635
00:39:15,710 --> 00:39:16,440
How did it go?

636
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:19,700
The Provincial Bureau leaders
coordinated everything.

637
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:20,410
The school has agreed

638
00:39:20,410 --> 00:39:22,190
that I can prioritize
the investigation work.

639
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:24,000
I'll be on temporary assignment
for one semester first,

640
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,710
and we'll see how it goes.

641
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:27,150
That's pretty good.

642
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,420
Let's go check out my office.

643
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:31,050
Let's go.

644
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,040
The photo looks nice.

645
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:39,460
Not as good as the real person though.

646
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:06,920
Professor Jiang,

647
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,660
can I borrow a couple of books?

648
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,000
I'll bring them
all to your place sometime.

649
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:13,320
That's not necessary.

650
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,630
I'm a slow reader.

651
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:16,700
Just lend me two books,

652
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:19,230
that preferably aren't too boring.

653
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:25,150
This one is about psychoanalysis.

654
00:40:25,150 --> 00:40:26,110
It's about women.

655
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:27,110
You might like it.

656
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:37,170
And this one.

657
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:38,920
I like it.

658
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:45,660
In Cold Blood.

659
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:50,060
It's a a crime investigation book

660
00:40:50,060 --> 00:40:51,270
that blends fiction

661
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,070
with factual record.

662
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,600
It even has a film adaption.

663
00:40:55,150 --> 00:40:56,230
Why do you like it?

664
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,070
Everyone might have

665
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:02,670
grown up in a small dark room.

666
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:05,840
Some choose to walk out
through the front door,

667
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:07,440
and others through the back.

668
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,670
They all should deserve sympathy,

669
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:12,480
but because of their different exits,

670
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:13,230
good and evil

671
00:41:13,350 --> 00:41:14,750
become clearly defined.

672
00:41:16,330 --> 00:41:17,730
Human nature is complex.

673
00:41:18,190 --> 00:41:20,190
I like this book's self-reflection

674
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,250
and compassion.

675
00:41:24,950 --> 00:41:26,280
I'll read it carefully.

676
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,120
Is class over?

677
00:41:34,110 --> 00:41:34,970
Yes, it's over.

678
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:40,490
It's already 11:50.

679
00:41:42,030 --> 00:41:42,760
What's this?

680
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,400
It's an old video

681
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,480
of my brother.

682
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,640
You can watch.

683
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:55,360
This was their competition.

684
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:57,010
My brother won first place.

685
00:41:57,190 --> 00:41:58,520
When was this recorded?

686
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:00,750
This was my brother's

687
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,510
last recorded video.

688
00:42:04,590 --> 00:42:05,650
It's an interview.

689
00:42:06,350 --> 00:42:07,040
It's recording.

690
00:42:07,040 --> 00:42:07,700
Recording.

691
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,550
Next on camera is

692
00:42:09,550 --> 00:42:11,550
the former Deputy Captain
of the Cheetah Strike Force,

693
00:42:11,550 --> 00:42:13,190
the champion of
the 13th Sniper Shooting Individual Event.

694
00:42:13,190 --> 00:42:14,110
Is that Zhao Ping?

695
00:42:14,110 --> 00:42:15,280
The best competitor

696
00:42:15,630 --> 00:42:17,670
and candidate
for Deputy Chief of the Special Police.

697
00:42:17,670 --> 00:42:18,760
This is too blurry.

698
00:42:18,780 --> 00:42:19,910
I can't see clearly.

699
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:21,160
The pride of our unit,

700
00:42:21,370 --> 00:42:22,730
Captain Zhou Chuan!

701
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:23,560
Applause!

702
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:24,400
Hooray!

703
00:42:36,860 --> 00:42:38,390
It does look like Zhao Ping.

704
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:40,840
Although the video is a bit blurry,

705
00:42:40,840 --> 00:42:42,900
a person's posture is hard to change.

706
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:45,320
Zhao Ping usually hunches his back,

707
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:46,760
with his left side

708
00:42:47,230 --> 00:42:48,590
slightly lower than the right.

709
00:42:48,590 --> 00:42:49,840
He also has uneven shoulders.

710
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,360
I see.

711
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,820
Hello, Senior.

712
00:42:53,590 --> 00:42:55,190
It really does seem to be him.

713
00:42:55,280 --> 00:42:56,810
But that's not surprising.

714
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:57,920
He and my brother

715
00:42:58,320 --> 00:42:59,520
were in the same unit.

716
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:06,590
Who's that person next to him?
